The troops of Operation LAKE SANITY today, neutralized several Boko Haram/ Islamic State West Africa Province (BH/ISWAP) terrorists in the Lake Chad axis. In a statement posted on the HQ Headquarters, the Army Facebook timeline added that troops also recovered weapons and equipment from terrorists. The statement further stated that Boko Haram/ISWAP Central Vehicle Fabrication Workshop & several bunkers were also discovered and destroyed. 